article_id:1187,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue with the Amount of Rupies Required to Craft Certain Void Weapons,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue where more than the intended amount of rupies are expended for certain Void weapons when using Craft, Enhance, or Dismantle under Crafting.</div><div>This issue was resolved in a data update at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585634400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Starting around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585639800"></span>, we will send all players who crafted affected weapons the difference between the rupies spent and the rupies that should have been required.</div><div>・If a player used materials obtained from the Cerulean Ghost, Lambent Ghost, or Violet Ghost to craft a tier two or tier three weapon directly from the tree, this will also apply to the amount of rupies consumed when crafting the tier one or tier two weapons.</div><div>・The gift will be sent to the goodie boxes of affected players.</div><div><br></div><div>■Affected Weapons and Details</div><div>1. Tier one weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Blazing Ghost, Cerulean Ghost, Lambent Ghost, or Violet Ghost</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Rest Eternal (3★/blade/unattuned)</div><div>・Heartseeker (3★/lance/unattuned)</div><div>・Mockery (3★/bow/unattuned)</div><div>・Clamor Wand (3★/wand/unattuned)</div><div><br></div><div>Rupies Consumed when Crafted</div><div>Incorrect: 3,000 rupies</div><div>Correct: 1,000 rupies</div><div><br></div><div>Rupies Consumed when Dismantled</div><div>Incorrect: 6,000 rupies</div><div>Correct: 2,000 rupies</div><div><br></div><div>2. Tier two weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Blazing Ghost</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Resentment (3★/blade/shadow)</div><div>・Quavering Bloodlust (3★/lance/shadow)</div><div>・Cacklemurk (3★/bow/shadow)</div><div>・Wickedheart (3★/wand/shadow)</div><div><br></div><div>Rupies Consumed when Enhanced</div><div>Incorrect: 15,000 rupies</div><div>Correct: 5,000 rupies</div><div><br></div><div>Rupies Consumed when Dismantled</div><div>Incorrect: 30,000 rupies</div><div>Correct: 10,000 rupies</div><div><br></div><div>3. Tier three weapons crafted using materials obtained from the Blazing Ghost</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Unwelcome Meeting (4★/blade/shadow)</div><div>・Spear of Tragedy (4★/lance/shadow)</div><div>・Howlshadow (4★/bow/shadow)</div><div>・Darkheart (4★/wand/shadow)</div><div><br></div><div>Rupies Consumed when Enhanced</div><div>Incorrect: 90,000 rupies</div><div>Correct: 30,000 rupies</div><div><br></div><div>Rupies Consumed when Dismantled</div><div>Incorrect: 180,000 rupies</div><div>Correct: 60,000 rupies</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div>,start_time:1585634400,update_time1585216347